OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled for Blackpool's
OL,4,Cmost famous clown
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes was at the unveiling
OL,8,Fof the plaque in Blackpool.
OL,10,FA blue plaque has been unveiled in
OL,11,FBlackpool to honour the legendary
OL,12,Fclown Charlie Cairoli.
OL,14,FThe seaside town became Charlie's
OL,15,Fadopted home after he moved there from
OL,16,FItaly in 1939.
OL,18,FHe became one of the most famous
OL,19,Fentertainers at the Tower Circus where
OL,20,Fhe performed for four decades.
