OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled for Blackpool's
OL,4,Cmost famous clown
OL,6,FThe Charlie Cairoli Appreciation
OL,7,FSociety, founded in 1994, continues to
OL,8,Fhonour Charlie's extraordinary
OL,9,Fcontribution to the performing arts
OL,10,Fand to Blackpool's cultural history.
OL,12,FNigel Male from the society said:
OL,13,F"Charlie brought more holidaymakers
OL,14,Finto Blackpool than any other
OL,15,Fentertainer.
OL,17,F"People would come year after year. He
OL,18,Fwas infamous for his slapstick comedy
OL,19,Fand, as a musician, he could play
OL,20,Fevery single instrument including a
OL,21,Fkitchen sink and a toilet seat."
