OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled for Blackpool's
OL,4,Cmost famous clown
OL,6,FNorman Barrett was the Ringmaster at
OL,7,Fthe Tower Circus when Charlie used to
OL,8,Fperform.
OL,10,F"The audience loved him", he said, "To
OL,11,Fwork with Charlie was wonderful. He
OL,12,Fwas the king of the circus and knew
OL,13,Fwhat the audience wanted and how to do
OL,14,Fit."
OL,16,FThe blue plaque will now be on show at
OL,17,Fthe Tower's front entrance as a
OL,18,Fpermanent memorial to the clown.
